                    <div class="chooseContent">
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="chooseMe">
                               1- Experience and Trustworthiness.
                            </h2>

                            <p class="choose">
                                Our company has been providing tour services since August 20, 2003 and we have gained a
                                good
                                reputation. More than 50 000 of tourist from all over the world have already travel with
                                us
                                and highly appreciated the level of service.
                            </p>
                            <h2 class="chooseMe">

                               2- Friendly and Qualified Stuff.
                            </h2>
                            <p class="choose">
                                All the members of our team are passionate about their work and always ready to help. We
