                                <div class="testimonialBox">
                                    <img src="../../img/quote.png" class="quote">
                                    <div class="content1">
                                        <p>Prompt and efficient service. Good communication. Great value for money package. Spoke with several consultants all who were able to assist.</p>
                                        <div class="details1">
                                            <div class="imgBx">
                                                <img src="../../img/ali.jpg" alt="">
